name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`BEGIN`,
t1.`CREATEDATE`,
t1.`CREATEMAN`,
t1.`DATE`,
t1.`END`,
t1.`IBIZPRO_PRODUCTDAILYID`,
t1.`IBIZPRO_PRODUCTDAILYNAME`,
t1.`PO`,
t1.`PRODUCT`,
t2.`NAME` AS `PRODUCTNAME`,
t1.`TASKS`,
t1.`TOTALESTIMATES`,
t1.`UPDATEDATE`,
t1.`UPDATEMAN`
FROM `T_IBIZPRO_PRODUCTDAILY` t1 
LEFT JOIN `ZT_PRODUCT` t2 ON t1.`PRODUCT` = t2.`ID`
